Vuelta Velogames Daily Update

Race Results - Stage 21




Many of you no doubt already know the result, but here’s the non-spoiler 5min highlight clip on Youtube:

https://youtu.be/Al48u4Rxk7M





Dutch sprinter Dylan Groenewegen provided an upset victory over the more established fast-man favourites on the Champs-Élysées ahead of André Greipel, the biggest win of his career. Edvald Boasson Hagen finished third. All the jersey winnners arrived at the finish line safely in the pack, with Chris Froome taking his fourth Tour De France win.



Results on cycling news:

Velogames Results - 4051 Rouleurs - Final


It’s worth pointing out the method used by Velogames for calculating points after the final stage. Velogames awards points in the normal manner for Stage 21, but then awards points using an imaginary Stage 22 for Bonus Points based on rider finishing positions in accordance with the game rules:

https://www.velogames.com/vuelta-a-espana/2017/scores.php
